OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRishi Sunak says future tax
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcuts depend on repairing   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpublic finances            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rishi Sunak has told Conservative party
OL,6, members that future tax cuts are       
OL,7, conditional on repairing the UK's      
OL,8, public finances after Covid.           
OL,10,FIn his first conference speech as      
OL,11,Fchancellor, he said he wanted lower    
OL,12,Ftaxes - but funding the pandemic       
OL,13,Frecovery "comes with a cost".          
OL,15,FVowing that "we need to fix our public 
OL,16,Ffinances", he said allowing borrowing  
OL,17,Fto rise further would be "immoral".    
OL,19,FThe comments come three weeks before   
OL,20,Fhis autumn Budget on 27 October.       
